      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">皇皇者華.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>皇皇者華，于彼原隰。駪駪征夫，每懷靡及。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Brilliant are the flowers,
On those level heights and the low grounds.
Complete and alert is the messenger, with his suite,
Ever anxious lest he should not succeed.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
