      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·003.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">皇皇者華.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我馬維駒，六轡如濡。載馳載驅，周爰咨諏。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My horses are young;
The six reins look as if they were moistened.
I gallop them, and urge them on,
Everywhere pushing my inquiries.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
