      <prop type="x-translation-ref">皇皇者華.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我馬維騏，六轡如絲。載馳載驅，周爰咨謀。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My horses are piebald;
The six reins are like silk.
I gallop them, and urge them on,
Everywhere seeking information and counsel.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
