      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我馬維駱，六轡沃若。載馳載驅，周爰咨度。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My horses are white and black-maned;
The six reins look glossy.
I gallop them and urge them on,
Everywhere seeking information and advice.</seg>
      </tuv>
