      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我馬維駰，六轡既均。載馳載驅，周爰咨詢。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>My horses are grey;
The six reins are well in hand.
I gallop them and urge them on,
Everywhere seeking information and suggestions.</seg>
      </tuv>
